data.name: AWS MQ
data.xml_template:
<route  id="{{source}}">
    <from uri="aws2-mq://{{hostname}}:{{port}}/{{queue}}{{querystring  query_params  extra_query_params}}%26queue%3D{{queue}}"/>
    {{applyUnmarshal output_format output_format_options}}
    {{applyMarshal output_format output_format_options}}
    {{generateDestination target}}
</route>
